    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Collection of texts in Arabic and Ottoman Turkish. After the first work, a large portion of the manuscript is prayers attributed to Abū al-Ḥasan ʻAlī al-Shādhilī with other, additional prayers and religious poetry. Main texts are copied in at least two hands with notes in additional hands.</subfield>
    </datafield>
