    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="505" ind1="0" ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">1. f. 1v-53v: Manāzil quṭb al-ʻārifīn wa manāzil aṣḥāb al-sālikīn -- 2. f. 55v-112r: [Prayers] / Abū al-Ḥasan ʻAlī al-Shādhilī -- 3. f. 112v-120v: Risālah -- 4. f. 123v-135r: [Prayer] -- 5. f. 135v-: Wird / Sayyid Yaḥyá -- 6. f. 140r-141v: Wird Mūllá al-Kūrānī -- 7. f. 142r-: Duʻāʹnāmah / Abū al-Saʻūd Afandī -- 8. f. 143v-161v: [Prayers] / Muḥammad ibn Muḥammad al-ʻArabī al-Khātimī al-Ṭāʼī al-Andalusī -- 9. f. 162v-165r: Duʻāʼ sharīf / Ṣadr al-Dīn Qūnawī -- 10. f. 166v-167r: Khawāṣṣ Ayat al-Kursī -- 11. f. 167v-169r: Munājāt / Muḥyī al-Dīn al-ʻArabī -- 12. Ḥizb /  Muḥyī al-Dīn al-ʻArabī -- 13. f. 171v-173v: Duʻāʼ al-Fātiḥah maʻ al-basmalah / al-Shaykh Muḥyī al-Dīn -- 14. f. 173v-174v: Ṣalāt ʻAbd al-Qādir al-Jīlānī -- 15. f. 175r-177v: Tables and notes</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Layout: 11 long lines.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Script: Written in naskh in black ink; pointed and partially vocalized.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Illuminated headpiece in gold, pink, yellow with blue and red foliate finials (f. 1v); textblock is border-ruled in two styles: gold, black, red (f. 1v-143r, 162v-164v), single red (f. 143v-161v); gold roundels with orange and blue dots punctuate the text; other simple headpieces in gold lined with black (f. 55v, 76v, 77v, 82v, 112v, 123v, 135v); diagram in black and red (f. 30v), table in black (f. 121v); rubrications in red, some headers set into gold bands (for example, f. 30r).</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Origin: A transmission note is dated 1212 AH (1797 CE) (f. 71r).</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Stamp with the name ʻUthmān (stamps, f. 147v).</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
